<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HP CSV Cleanup Tool</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>HP CSV Cleanup Tool</h1>
            <p>Upload your HP CSV file to automatically clean and filter the data</p>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="upload-section">
                <div class="upload-area" id="uploadArea">
                    <div class="upload-content">
                        <svg class="upload-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path>
                            <polyline points="7,10 12,15 17,10"></polyline>
                            <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
                        </svg>
                        <h3>Drop your CSV files here</h3>
                        <p>or click to browse (you can select multiple files)</p>
                        <input type="file" id="fileInput" accept=".csv" style="display: none;" multiple>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="processing-section" id="processingSection" style="display: none;">
                <div class="progress-container">
                    <h3>Processing your file...</h3>
                    <div class="progress-bar">
                        <div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div>
                    </div>
                    <p id="progressText">Step 1: Reading file...</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="results-section" id="resultsSection" style="display: none;">
                <div class="results-header">
                    <h3>Processing Complete!</h3>
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;">
                        <button class="download-btn" id="downloadBtn">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path>
                                <polyline points="7,10 12,15 17,10"></polyline>
                                <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line>
                            </svg>
                            Download Cleaned CSV
                        </button>
                        <button class="download-btn" id="clearBtn" style="background: #e53e3e;">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                                <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
                                <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
                            </svg>
                            Clear Results
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h4>Original Rows</h4>
                        <p id="originalRows">0</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h4>Filtered Rows</h4>
                        <p id="filteredRows">0</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h4>Removed Duplicates</h4>
                        <p id="removedDuplicates">0</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <h4>Final Rows</h4>
                        <p id="finalRows">0</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="preview-section">
                    <h4>Preview of Cleaned Data</h4>
                    <div class="table-container">
                        <table id="previewTable">
                            <thead id="previewHeader"></thead>
                            <tbody id="previewBody"></tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="emptyFilesList" style="display:none; margin-top:2rem;">
                    <h4>Files with No Matching Rows</h4>
                    <ul id="emptyFilesUl" style="color:#e53e3e;"></ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <h3>What this tool does:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Removes the first row (header cleanup)</li>
                    <li>Deletes columns F and G</li>
                    <li>Filters for "Dark Fiber - LH" or "Dark Fiber - Metro" in column 6</li>
                    <li>Filters for specific companies (Google, Amazon, Meta, etc.) in column 7</li>
                    <li>Inserts a new column D</li>
                    <li>Removes duplicates based on column 3</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 